          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Zr-nat foils, 10 mum as targets, Ti-nat foils, 10 mum",
                "acting as a monitor, placed in front of each target",
                "and Al foils, 10, 20, 100 mum, placed after each target",
                "foil, acting both as catcher for recoils particles and",
                "energy degrader, were used. Zr-96 is only 2.8% of",
                "natural Zr targets, the irradiation time was about 4 hr",
                "long."
